text: Ibrahim Bin Khalil () is a Bangladeshi Jatiya Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Chittagong-14. ==Career== Khalil was elected to parliament from Chittagong-14 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1986 and 1988. He was a member of the Chittagong Division Sub-Committee. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
